== Battle Commands ==

=== Attack ===

Physical strike with equipped weapon.
* Damage based on Strength and weapon
* Can target single enemy
* Midenhall Prince's primary action

=== Spell ===

Cast learned magic:

{| class="wikitable"
! Category !! Examples
|-
| Heal || Restore HP
|-
| Hurt || Direct damage
|-
| Status || Buff/debuff
|-
| Travel || Warp, Return
|}

=== Item ===

Use inventory item:
* Medical Herb - Heal HP
* Antidote - Cure poison
* Wing of Wyvern - Escape dungeon

=== Defend ===

Take defensive stance:
* Reduces damage taken
* Useful when low on HP

=== Flee ===

Attempt to escape battle:
* Success not guaranteed
* Harder against tough enemies

